{"tid":1675566,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解個政府解決唔到依家香港既問題 ?","createTime":"2019-10-26T03:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T04:02:58.000Z","uid":69864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4597aefe4b4e5ac5e9389edfc6d9a17e30c5420c","tid":1675566,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">長文,懶就睇睇Highligh重點</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">=========前言=========</div></strong></span><br />\n[/u][/b]<div style=\"text-align: center;\">在香港長大既咁多位<br />\n由細到大都對香港政府既垃圾文宣設計<br />\n應該都深有感觸<br />\n特別係幾年前出到黎開設計相關既公司,一聽到個客係政府?<br />\nOK 報貴3到4倍先應該都係國際通例<br />\n報貴幾倍有好多原因,但無非都係呢幾個:<br />\n要照顧弱智、個政府乞我憎、成品無可能做到Portfolio<br />\n同埋班友真係唔撚知咩叫想象力,你要花十倍時間同佢解釋</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">=========前設=========</div></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">想像力</span>其實<span style=\"color: orange;\">係同理心既<span style=\"color: red;\">基本要求</span></span><br />\n因為<span style=\"color: orange;\">無想像力 = <span style=\"color: red;\">感受唔同對方既痛</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>:點解正常人睇恐怖片會驚?<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">A</span>:因為我地代入到主角</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>:咩人會一畢業就出黎做政府工做官做警犬?<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">A</span>:咪就係想像唔到自己未來果堆人囉</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">因為佢地只可以睇到依家有咩工可以帶比自己最大既利益<br />\n最慘既係<span style=\"color: orange;\">本身佢地已經係想像力低下</span>,<br />\n仲要入埋<span style=\"color: orange;\">政府</span>呢個<span style=\"color: orange;\">會進一步降低你想像意欲</span>既地方</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">=========日常例子=========</div></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">其實我只係善意提醒佢少少常識性既錯誤</span><br />\n但佢地通常只會識得答你:</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「啊...我問下上頭先」<br />\n「啊...我唔清楚呀,呢單野唔係我跟」<br />\n「啊...我地一直以黎都係咁做架」</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>:點解佢地唔會理我?只係推個波出去?<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">佢地唔驚犯錯奶野比上頭屌?</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">A</span>:<strong>NOOOOO!</strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">係因為佢地想像唔到,唔聽我講原來會奶野</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">所以大家可以睇到,點解政府堆PR成日出事<br />\n明明咁多錢請人,<br />\n唔係因為佢外判請返黎班人廢<br />\n係因為佢地個架構只會容許你服從上級<br />\n唔會容許你思考同想像答案<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後奶左野佢地先會意識到自己奶左野</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">=========總結=========</div></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家呢個正正就係香港既現況</span><br />\n一早有人同佢地講咁樣會奶野<br />\n但呢幾個月以黎<br />\n<strong>你估佢地唔想解決件事?</strong><br />\n但係......<span style=\"color: red;\">點解一直都解決唔到呀?</span><br />\n因為佢地<span style=\"color: orange;\">無想像力</span>呀<br />\n咁......<span style=\"color: red;\">點解一直Keep住有警暴?</span><br />\n因為佢地<span style=\"color: orange;\">無良知</span>呀</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">特別係隻777</span>, 呢世人只係做過政府工, 連個政客都算唔上<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">政府工之王</span> <strong>  點會有能力判斷到自己做過既野會有咩後果?</strong><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1234b87318e33882bf58700a25259a43b5f6bf10","tid":1675566,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"溫習題:<br />\n<strong>點解班狗唔知自己係CONDOM? </strong><br />\n<br />\n大家識答未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8bcdc64b37797f28807ab548766838fc482994","tid":1675566,"uid":87498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1234b87318e33882bf58700a25259a43b5f6bf10","tid":1675566,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"溫習題:<br />\n<strong>點解班狗唔知自己係CONDOM? </strong><br />\n<br />\n大家識答未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"點會唔知?就係知先會咁,係咪都要死,緊係同你攬炒"},{"pid":"e53e74bb680f664ca57df28e566925de4fa87b95","tid":1675566,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b8bcdc64b37797f28807ab548766838fc482994","tid":1675566,"uid":87498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1234b87318e33882bf58700a25259a43b5f6bf10","tid":1675566,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"溫習題:<br />\n<strong>點解班狗唔知自己係CONDOM? </strong><br />\n<br />\n大家識答未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"點會唔知?就係知先會咁,係咪都要死,緊係同你攬炒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"醒少少既就69前離隊啦<br />\n再醒啲既就雨傘後就走人啦<br />\n依家留低既,咪就係當初諗唔到依家會搞成咁<br />\n咪唯有扮唔知,做落去囉<br />\n換句話說,即係已經濕左水,<br />\n所以你講得岩,佢地冇得揀,只可以同我地攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過今日仲未走既人應該都冇想像到既係,<br />\n依家走都可能仲有一線生機呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb24da708cce82c1458f16d900f2180e298d3133","tid":1675566,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"大陸人優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}